text: Tisha Campbell (born October 13, 1968) is an American television actress. She played Gina Waters in the series Martin (August 1992 - May 1997). She also played Sydney in the House Party movies. Campbell was born in Oklahoma City, though raised in Newark, New Jersey. ==References== Category:Actors from Oklahoma Category:American television actors Category:1968 births Category:Living people
